{"tid":1331848,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[京阿尼]中國fans在twitter說「加油」「祝福」等字句 被日本網友誤解","createTime":"2019-07-19T05:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T22:42:01.000Z","uid":150609,"like":26,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bc595e34f42af149bce0382cd457b84b0d46a65e","tid":1331848,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXp2RDn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXp2RDn.png&h=dc667c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p70Q0wG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp70Q0wG.png&h=ca3637c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國語圈說加油 不謹慎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 火上加油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 日本網友解釋「加油」是頑張れ 応援の意味 沒有惡意的<br />\n「祝福」也不要生氣 是代表祈る 祈福<br />\n日本語「祝ＯＯ」 是「祝賀即將會發生事情」<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcGpkwP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcGpkwP.png&h=97caf135&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n語源是 讀書到深夜在油燈加油 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ir9Vscr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fir9Vscr.png&h=5f6e0b85&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">確かにガソリンばらまき放火に対して<br />\n加油はむちゃくちゃ勘違いしやすい字面だな<br />\n仕方ないけど<br />\n<br />\n的確對汽油放火事件 加油會被人誤會 沒有辨法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文字通り火に油を注ぐ発言かと思ったら<br />\nめっちゃ良い人達で感動した <br />\n<br />\n以為是字面上的火上加油的發言<br />\n知道後覺得很感動 都是好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n中日友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc3efe921f20364306f0f93e0490e9895e654fe","tid":1331848,"uid":90457,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"漢字差異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\"